---
import { SITE_NAME, SITE_TAGLINE } from '../consts';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-28 rule-double bg-paper">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-10 px-4 py-14 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr]">
    <div>
      <div class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">{SITE_NAME}</div>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">
        {SITE_TAGLINE}跨链、DeFi、稳定币与钱包安全，用大白话讲清楚，
        希望对同样在探索 Web3 的你有帮助。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">栏目</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink">
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/tags/跨链">跨链 / 跨链桥</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/tags/DeFi">DeFi</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/tags/稳定币">稳定币</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/tags/钱包安全">钱包安全</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">站点</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink">
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/blog">全部文章</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/about">关于本站</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-accent" href="/rss.xml">RSS 订阅</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-line py-6 text-center font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
    © {year} {SITE_NAME} · 仅供科普与学习 · 不构成投资建议
  </div>
</footer>
